PanelC graphs are generated by visualizing pairwise comparisons between NPC_wt-NPC_Δprom,  NPC_wt-NPC_polyA, and ESC_wt-ESC_Pax6+, produced with DEseq2.
The input for panelC graphs are log2foldchange and padj values as provided in Supplementary Table 2 (DEseq2 output):
- Sheet 4 NPC wt vs. NPC Δprom
- Sheet 5 NPC wt vs. NPC polyA
- Sheet 9 ESC wt vs. ESC Pax6+
